---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="HVAC Services in McDade, TX | String Prairie Heating & Air"
	description="Local heating and air conditioning services in McDade, Texas. Family-owned HVAC company providing installation, repair, and maintenance in McDade and surrounding Bastrop County."
>
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>HVAC Services in McDade, TX</h1>
			<p>Your local heating and air conditioning experts</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="area-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="area-intro">
				<h2>Serving McDade with Expert HVAC Services</h2>
				<p class="lead">
					McDade is a historic small town in Bastrop County with deep Texas roots, and String Prairie Heating & Air is proud to serve its residents with professional heating and cooling services. From the charming homes near downtown McDade to the ranches and farms along Highway 290, we understand the unique HVAC needs of this tight-knit community and are committed to keeping McDade families comfortable year-round.
				</p>
				<p class="lead">
					Whether you need a new system installed, emergency repairs during extreme Texas weather, or regular maintenance to keep your HVAC running efficiently, our experienced technicians are ready to help. We serve McDade and the surrounding areas including properties near Elgin and throughout northern Bastrop County.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="areas-served">
				<h3>Areas We Serve in McDade</h3>
				<p>
					We provide HVAC services throughout the McDade community including properties along Highway 290, homes in downtown McDade, ranches and farms in the McDade area, rural properties near FM 1441, and all surrounding countryside. Our service area also includes nearby Elgin, making us well-positioned to serve all of northern Bastrop County.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="services-overview">
				<h2>Complete HVAC Services for McDade Homes & Businesses</h2>
				<div class="services-list">
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Air Conditioning</h3>
						<p>AC installation, repair, maintenance, and emergency service to keep you cool during hot Texas summers.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Heating Systems</h3>
						<p>Furnace and heat pump installation, repair, and maintenance for comfortable winters.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Maintenance Plans</h3>
						<p>Preventive maintenance to extend system life, improve efficiency, and prevent breakdowns.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Emergency Service</h3>
						<p>Fast response when you need it most - we understand HVAC emergencies can't wait.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="local-advantages">
				<h2>Why McDade Residents Choose String Prairie</h2>
				<ul class="advantage-list">
					<li>Family-owned and operated - we understand small-town values</li>
					<li>Fast response times throughout Bastrop County</li>
					<li>Experience with historic homes and modern construction</li>
					<li>Honest, transparent pricing with no hidden fees</li>
					<li>Fully licensed and insured for your protection</li>
					<li>Expert knowledge of Central Texas climate challenges</li>
					<li>Quality workmanship backed by solid warranties</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="map-section">
				<h2>Find Us on the Map</h2>
				<p class="map-subtitle">Serving McDade and all of Bastrop County</p>
				<div class="map-container">
					<iframe
						src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d13796.84!2d-97.25!3d30.28!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x8644d8c8c8c8c8c9%3A0xabababababababab!2sMcDade%2C%20TX%2078650!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1234567890"
						width="100%"
						height="450"
						style="border:0; border-radius: 12px;"
						allowfullscreen=""
						loading="lazy"
						referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
					</iframe>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="testimonials-section">
				<h2>What McDade Customers Say</h2>
				<p class="testimonials-subtitle">Hear from your neighbors about their experience with String Prairie Heating & Air</p>
				<div class="testimonials-grid">
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"Hard to find good HVAC service out here in McDade, but String Prairie is the real deal. Ron and his team are honest, professional, and do quality work. Highly recommend!"</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- William P., McDade</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"Our old farmhouse needed a complete HVAC upgrade. String Prairie handled everything professionally and worked with our budget. The new system works great!"</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- Dorothy & Frank H., McDade</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"Called for an emergency repair on a Sunday and they came out same day. That's the kind of service you just don't find anymore. We're customers for life!"</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- Randy S., McDade</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="review-cta">
					<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/String+Prairie+Heating+%26+Air/@29.8918229,-97.3320232" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="review-link">Leave us a Google Review</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section-local">
				<h2>Schedule Your HVAC Service in McDade</h2>
				<p>Ready for reliable HVAC service from your local experts? Contact us today!</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<a href="https://book.housecallpro.com/book/String-Prairie-Heating--Air/df82ded280ce43f4a9ee6ee6d36aef76?v2=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Book Online</a>
					<a href="tel:5129249744" class="btn btn-secondary">Call (512) 924-9744</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-blue) 0%, var(--primary-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 5rem 0;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.page-header p {
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		opacity: 0.95;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.area-content {
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}

	.area-intro {
		max-width: 850px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.area-intro h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.lead {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.areas-served {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, var(--dark-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.areas-served h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.areas-served p {
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
		opacity: 0.95;
	}

	.services-overview {
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	.services-overview h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.services-list {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.service-item {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-red);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.service-item:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.12);
		border-left-color: var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.service-item h3 {
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.service-item p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.local-advantages {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	.local-advantages h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.advantage-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		max-width: 750px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.advantage-list li {
		padding: 1rem 0 1rem 2.5rem;
		position: relative;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		font-weight: 300;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.1);
	}

	.advantage-list li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.advantage-list li:before {
		content: "âœ“";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--accent-red);
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.map-section {
		margin: 4rem 0;
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		background: var(--bg-light);
		border-radius: 12px;
	}

	.map-section h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.map-subtitle {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.map-container {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.testimonials-section {
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	.testimonials-section h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.testimonials-subtitle {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.testimonials-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.testimonial-card {
		background: white;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
		border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-red);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.testimonial-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.12);
		border-left-color: var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.stars {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		color: #f59e0b;
	}

	.testimonial-text {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.testimonial-author {
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.review-cta {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.review-link {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, var(--dark-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 50px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.3);
	}

	.review-link:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.4);
	}

	.cta-section-local {
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-red) 0%, var(--dark-red) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}

	.cta-section-local h2 {
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.cta-section-local p {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		opacity: 0.95;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.btn {
		padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		display: inline-block;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: white;
		color: var(--accent-red);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background: transparent;
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid white;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		background: white;
		color: var(--accent-red);
		transform: translateY(-3px);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-header h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.area-intro h2,
		.services-overview h2,
		.local-advantages h2,
		.map-section h2,
		.testimonials-section h2,
		.cta-section-local h2 {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}

		.services-list {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.map-section {
			padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.testimonials-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
